Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.73,0:00:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一是一之宫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.87,0:00:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二是日光的东照宫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.47,0:00:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三是樱花的宗五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.18,0:00:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…好慢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思!可是今天钓到的鱼好多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看和麻子的爷爷,两个人钓到这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋!笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.36,0:00:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼还在跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.57,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.02,0:01:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为什么又想把这么古老的水车转起来？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次来乡下时就在想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如能把这水车转动的话不知道有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.27,0:01:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没想到还要陪女生一起漫浪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是漫浪而是浪漫…浪漫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转动了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一是一之宫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二是日光的东照宫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三是樱花的宗五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潮与虎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:23.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来へと延びてる 道はただ遠くて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:35.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺の夢　じゃまする ヤツらでいっぱい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:43.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙に　Good Luck　別れを告げて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:53.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歩いてゆくのさ　明日へ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:56.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,両手に Fight Mind 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:04:06.37,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇気をたばねて 前を向いてゆくだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.42,0:04:09.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fighter hope a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:20.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰にも負けない 輝きを抱きしめたい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转轮疾走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成我的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画画到天亮,好想睡觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我的创作干劲连我自己都觉得吃不消
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是创作干劲,画的画都是很差劲的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小潮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安…小潮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻子她最近情况不太好,老是在做奇怪的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是梦见被熊吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要做那样的梦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为麻子所作的梦都是吃东西的梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是熊就是象或马吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个男人婆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要睡迷糊了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻子,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没有什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢吞吞的话可是会迟到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子曰学而时习之不亦说乎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朋自远方来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不亦乐乎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:08:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是持有兽之矛男人的血统吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆一口气…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑贱的东西!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于被我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…麻子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成我的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌!怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这种常常在发呆的人还可能\N麻子怎么会看见这种幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:09:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊!假如这种事情如果被小潮知道的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知他会怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…真由子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说曹操曹操就到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的理科实验报告借给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小潮你再睡觉的话,回家的功课就会越来越多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小潮!我最讨厌你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一碰头就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实在的刚才的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如告诉小潮的话\N不知他会怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成我的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻…麻子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中村麻子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是幻影!你是什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂麻子…究竟是怎么回事!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就是你重要的朋友吧\N看了你的眼神我就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们杀掉的话,你就不会在留恋这里的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.31,0:10:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…把真由子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是住在六年前你注入生命的水车小屋里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从那个时候就开始找你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从那以后就没有再去过水车小屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…水车小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一是一之宫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二是日光的东照宫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三是樱花宗五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.03,0:11:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在乡下的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你在一起生活,要你再来帮我转动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中村麻子跟着我来吧,请你让我永远转动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!不要!这种事我绝对不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不这么做的话,我就把对你重要的人一个一个杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连那个女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那个男的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻子那家伙不管问她什么\N都装没听到连一句话都不说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由子也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:13:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楼上的门转着掉下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是睡一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物?怎么可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋…你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那家伙为什么住在会转的东西里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天在学校附在女人身上的家妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是怎么一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在麻子身上吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我一起这么久,还不知道这种事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?麻子身上附有什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做圆的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.52,0:13:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲在会转动的东西里,体味怪异的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙为什么会在麻子身上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:14:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能在什么地方,她让什么古老的东西转动了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在那个地方的家伙,可能是对她一见钟情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻…麻子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚好要去你那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.14,0:14:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小潮…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该更加振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙说这种话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你这种人…你这种人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小潮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为麻子说一定要向你告别所以才带她来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.19,0:15:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做圆的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开麻子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答应的事我会遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.10,0:15:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要带我到哪我都会跟你去\N所以…所以…请不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要做这种事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该早一点说不就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说废话了快来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀原来你是妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有许多原因,你快把那女孩放下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…这个下流家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎!你要干什么,不要随便出手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他先向我挑衅的,怎么可以让他逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…兽之矛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放开麻子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻子是…我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会把她交给任何人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻子…一起到很远地方生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你替我转动着,永远的生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家伙不要太得意了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!妖怪会胜过用铁做的列车吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.22,0:19:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀？你是什么呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我死也不会放手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会放开她的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里罗嗦什么,小潮!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.03,0:21:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我来收拾这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.03,0:21:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了这个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻子会哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手我会信守诺言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要带我去哪都跟你去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再伤害他了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:22:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白他不是坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.96,0:22:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.56,0:22:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你这样的男人保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.80,0:22:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来没有我存在的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.47,0:22:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一是一之宫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.34,0:22:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二是日光的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.92,0:22:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你是住在麻子乡下家的古老水车里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.86,0:22:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有份帮水车转动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.80,0:22:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是麻子强迫我的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.63,0:22:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.27,0:23:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样…也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.94,0:23:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.32,0:23:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.26,0:23:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一是一之宫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.46,0:23:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二是日光的东照宫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.17,0:23:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三是樱花的宗五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.14,0:23:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害…麻子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.08,0:23:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候我外婆教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.42,0:23:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下你还没说清楚上回\N梦中的怪男人是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.19,0:24:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…那只是功课压力太大\N胡思乱而想做的怪梦而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧,小潮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.00,0:24:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道,笨蛋会有什么功课压力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.77,0:24:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.38,0:24:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么资格骂我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.21,0:24:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.48,0:24:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛死了,你干什么,男人婆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么,我今天一定不放过你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.92,0:24:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人婆…\N你再讲…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.03,0:25:02.60,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふたり選んだ道は　違っているけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.86,0:25:14.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢をまっすぐ見つめる瞳　同じだから
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.52,0:25:20.87,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何も言わなくてもわかる
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.50,0:25:27.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泣きたいほどツライ夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.36,0:25:32.82,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わざと笑いあい
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.35,0:25:39.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ただそばにいるだけさ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.99,0:25:45.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dear my best friend
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.43,0:25:50.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵐のように過ぎる　時代のなかで
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.38,0:25:54.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,変わらぬものがある
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.84,0:25:57.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dear my best friend
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.25,0:26:05.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺はいつも　その夢の味方でいる
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.89,0:26:27.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱いこのときめきを伝える　そのために
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.47,0:26:29.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're my best friend
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.67,0:26:40.44,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと俺とおまえの心が　出逢ったのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.48,0:26:46.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒野わたる風のように
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.98,0:26:52.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲しみさえ越えてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.98,0:26:58.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺はここにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.00,0:27:05.87,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そうさ　ひとりじゃないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.78,0:27:11.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dear my best friend
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.19,0:27:14.66,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負けそうになったなら
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.70,0:27:20.60,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思い出せよ おまえを 信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.61,0:27:22.92,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dear my best friend
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.99,0:27:31.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どんなときも　大切な友達だから


